WEBVTT

00:00:00.822 --> 00:00:07.835
mir hobn geredt vegn dem vos di tsvey amerikaner soldatn hobn avekgenumen di revolvern fun ayer kop.

00:00:07.538 --> 00:00:15.125
ya, avekgenumen di revolvern un zey hobn ongehoybn rufn un fayfn nokh eynemen. iz eyner tsugekumen, a vayser ofitsir,

00:00:15.570 --> 00:00:18.956
un er redt tsu mir, zogt er, ver bistu?

00:00:20.143 --> 00:00:24.845
zog ikh, ikh bin, zog ikh, a JEWISH BOY fun POLAND.

00:00:25.307 --> 00:00:29.756
ikh bin avek fun Oyshvits un ikh bin geven do oyf ander lagern.

00:00:30.403 --> 00:00:36.337
ikh bin arayngekumen do tsu di mentshn un zey hobn mikh oysbahaltn do biz yetst, biz ir zent gekumen.

00:00:37.947 --> 00:00:43.475
vos far a shprakh redstu? redstu, zogt er, er hot geredt tsu mir daytsh. zog ikh red daytsh.

00:00:43.718 --> 00:00:49.174
vos nokh redstu? zog ikh, du redst yidish? zog ikh, yo. red tsu mir in yidish.

00:00:49.174 --> 00:00:55.423
hob ikh gezogt yidish. ikh bin arayngekumen do tsu zey. zey hobn mikh oysbahaltn un zenen geven zeyer gut tsu mir.

00:00:56.442 --> 00:01:02.257
zogt er, ikh bin oykh a yid. hob ikh shoyn ongehoybn tsu veynen. un er hot geveynt.

00:01:03.681 --> 00:01:07.269
zogt er, "yingele, ales vet zayn in ordenung. du kumst yetst mit mir."

00:01:07.714 --> 00:01:14.525
zogt er tsu dem balbos, er nemt mikh tsu. zogn zey, neyn. zey hobn mikh oysbahaltn, mir viln er zol do blaybn bay undz.

00:01:14.970 --> 00:01:23.877
hot er gebetn, er ken nisht blaybn yetst. di ale velder zenen ful mit S.S., s'nokh nisht CLEAR. er darf kumen mit undz.

00:01:23.877 --> 00:01:30.675
mir veln im ophitn vet dir nisht fargesn, er vet tsu dir kumen. ikh bin take gekumen yedes mol, VISITn, vet er kumen VISITN, er vet tsu aykh kumen.

00:01:30.883 --> 00:01:33.425
er veyst az du host im opgetun a guts.

00:01:33.904 --> 00:01:42.234
un er hot mikh genumen avek in vald arayn. Dzhek! Mek! un genumen rufn ale genereler, ALL groyse ofitsirn, yidn.

00:01:42.325 --> 00:01:43.956
m'hot mir gemakht a SHOWER,

00:01:44.670 --> 00:01:52.747
m'hot mikh ongetun amerikaner kleyder. ikh hob gebetn dos ershte bayn im, gib mir a por shikh. zogt er, "yingele, ales vestu krign, kum mit mir."

00:01:53.074 --> 00:01:57.590
ir gedenkt umgefer vos a date s'iz gevezn demolts ir zayt bafrayt gevorn?

00:01:57.343 --> 00:02:02.214
demolts iz geven a date vos Minkhn iz nokh nisht geven genumen. Minkhn iz nokh geven di daytshn.

00:02:02.085 --> 00:02:03.598
in vos a monat umgefer?

00:02:04.296 --> 00:02:10.246
in s'hot gekent zayn demolts ikh veys efsher APRIL. far APRIL, APRIL.

00:02:10.675 --> 00:02:12.002
u- un ven,

00:02:11.232 --> 00:02:13.285
Minkhn no- Minkhn iz nokh nisht geven genumen.

00:02:13.594 --> 00:02:14.988
nokh nisht geven bafrayt.

00:02:14.488 --> 00:02:15.710
nokh nisht geven bafrayt.

00:02:15.619 --> 00:02:20.000
un di dem nomen fun di daytshn, di di di mishpokhe vos hot aykh geholfn,

00:02:19.500 --> 00:02:20.135
ye,

00:02:20.074 --> 00:02:21.907
veyst ir di mishpokhe nomen?

00:02:21.880 --> 00:02:27.065
ikh ho- ikh bin shoyn lang nisht gekumen tsu zey. s'dokh shoyn fuftsik yor adurkh, ober

00:02:27.065 --> 00:02:31.188
SURE veys ikh vu tsu forn. az ikh kum on haynt keyn Daytshland ken ikh visn glaykh tsutsuforn tsu zey.

00:02:30.942 --> 00:02:32.826
ober zeyer nomen gedenkt ir nisht?

00:02:32.477 --> 00:02:33.208
y- neyn.

00:02:33.208 --> 00:02:37.500
vi lang ikh bin gevezn dortn bin ikh yedes mol tsugeforn tsu zey. vi lang ikh bin geven in Daytshland.

00:02:37.911 --> 00:02:42.500
ANYWAYS hot er gen- genumen, er hot mikh arayngefirt, m'hot mikh opgevashn mikh

00:02:42.522 --> 00:02:48.454
in vald, m'hot mikh ongetun amerikaner kleyder, mit shikh, mit alem. yeder eyner hot mir gegebn a por dolar in tash arayn, mit a tayster.

00:02:48.454 --> 00:02:51.227
m'hot mikh ongetun a brandzelet, m'hot mir gegebn a zeyger,

00:02:51.227 --> 00:02:54.636
un ongetun a brandzelet oyf der hant, a gevorn a gantser amerikaner.

00:02:54.636 --> 00:02:59.693
zogt zi mir der ofitsir, "morgn darf vern Minkhn genumen.

00:02:59.693 --> 00:03:05.608
morgn vet faln Minkhn," zogt er, vet men araynforn in shtot arayn, ikh vel dikh arayngebn, zogt er, in a plats,

00:03:05.608 --> 00:03:10.119
vu du vest dikh erhoyln dikh. ikh hob gevoygn demolts draysik kilo.

00:03:13.517 --> 00:03:17.915
un azoy iz es gevezn, tsu morgns, un ikh bin geven mit zey, m'hot mir gegebn

00:03:18.057 --> 00:03:26.423
vos tsu esn nisht keyn SPECIAL, vayl vayl a sakh zenen avekgegangen fun esn bald toyt. ober m'hot mir gege- gegebn nor vos nor tsu derkhapn dos harts.

00:03:26.423 --> 00:03:29.086
zogt er, "morgn vestu ales visn vos du darfst esn."

00:03:29.110 --> 00:03:36.832
tsu morgns tsvey a zeyger kumt a PHONE CALL, Minkhn iz gevorn genumen, durkh di amerikaner, bafrayt.

00:03:36.832 --> 00:03:42.432
iz aroysgegangen di SHAYAROT, aroysgeforn ale di tanken, ikh bin geforn mit dem ofitsir bay im in Dzhip

00:03:42.432 --> 00:03:45.266
biz m'iz arayngekumen keyn Minkhn. m'iz arayngekumen keyn Minkhn,

00:03:45.266 --> 00:03:51.433
iz er gegangen zukhn dem plats vu arayntsugebn mikh, un er hot getrofn dem plats, vayl dortn zenen arayngekumen oykhet amerikaner tsu erhoyln zikh,

00:03:51.433 --> 00:03:55.599
vos zey hobn farloyrn a sakh vog un azoy vayter, zenen geven opgeshvakht,

00:03:55.599 --> 00:04:03.433
zenen oykh dortn arayngekumen. ikh geb a kum arum, un get a kum zitsn mit dem firer fun der HOSPITAL, iz oykhet dortn, geyt er a f- a fartekh, ver veyst dokh ver dos iz.

00:04:03.489 --> 00:04:05.809
zogt er, PAPER, PAPER.

00:04:05.809 --> 00:04:11.466
zogt er mir der amerikaner tsu im, zog nisht keyn PAPER, er iz nisht keyn amerikaner. ikh bin gegangen ongetun amerikaner kleyder.

00:04:11.541 --> 00:04:20.975
zogt er iz a a yid fun Poyln vos iz bafrayt fun Oyshvits. mir hobn im bafrayt. mir hobn im getrofn in zayn PASIAK mit alem.

00:04:20.975 --> 00:04:25.675
m'hot ongetun amerikaner kleyder. "oyb azoy yingele, kum aher." redt er oykh tsu mir yidish.

00:04:25.675 --> 00:04:30.951
un leygt mikh avek un zogt on di ale shvesters zey zoln afile nisht aropgegangen vegn TOILET, az m'zol alts far mir tun.

00:04:31.699 --> 00:04:33.887
er iz geven a yid fun vanen iz er gevezn?

00:04:33.707 --> 00:04:34.882
oykh amerikaner yid.

00:04:34.382 --> 00:04:35.354
amerikaner.

00:04:35.192 --> 00:04:37.464
a dokter. amerikaner.

00:04:37.572 --> 00:04:40.640
un er hot bahandlt di ale amerikaner un er hot bahandlt mikh,

00:04:40.680 --> 00:04:45.680
hob ikh gezogt tsum dokter, "lomikh shoyn aroys, lomikh zen di mapole fun di daytshn." zogt er, yingele, zogt er,

00:04:45.680 --> 00:04:51.160
"ikh vel dikh aroyslozn ven ikh vel dir zogn gey. vi lang ikh zog nisht get vestu do zayn.

00:04:51.160 --> 00:04:53.660
un du vest mikh gedenken dos gantse lebn.

00:04:53.704 --> 00:05:01.758
ikh vil dikh oysheyln un makhn hundert protsentik. ikh vil dir aroysnemen dem gantse vorem fun Oyshvits, un aroysnemen fun dir ales."

00:05:01.758 --> 00:05:11.175
du torst nisht, un dan hot er mir gegebn a DIET dos yo, un dos haynt yo, un dos nisht, un dos yo. un biz ikh gelign dortn fir vokhn, bin ikh aroys a yung.

00:05:11.175 --> 00:05:15.402
a gantser SOLDIER. un er iz gekumen der ofitsir mikh yedn tog bafr- yedn tog mir VISITn.

00:05:15.402 --> 00:05:20.361
un ikh bin aroysgekumen hob ho- hot er mir, bin ikh bay im geven bay im in der TZAVA, bay dem in der ARMY,

00:05:20.383 --> 00:05:22.385
oykhet epes a por khadoshim,

00:05:22.392 --> 00:05:28.607
un di muter hot mir geshribn bald, azoy vi er hot geshribn a brivele aheym az er hot bafrayt a yidishn boytshik fun Poyln fun Oyshvits,

00:05:28.607 --> 00:05:32.156
hob ikh di mame gebetn a por shikh, fun vanet hot er gevust az er hot shikh.

00:05:32.179 --> 00:05:37.320
hot zi mir geshikt a pak mit esn mit trinken mit shokolad mit ale gute zakhn, un do a por shikh.

00:05:37.377 --> 00:05:39.565
zogt er na dir, di mame hot dir geshikt a por shikh.

00:05:40.077 --> 00:05:41.556
ir gedenkt zayn nomen?

00:05:42.051 --> 00:05:44.053
ir gedenkt zayn nomen, der ofits-

00:05:42.945 --> 00:05:45.979
ver vi an ⟨yidishn⟩ briv ⟨gefinen⟩ azoy fil yorn.

00:05:45.979 --> 00:05:54.560
un er hot mir gezogt mir efsher vilstu mitforn? zog ikh, NO, un vi ken ikh avekforn avekforn, tomer ikh vil dokh geyn FAMILY, ikh vil dokh geyn, efsher iz geblibn a bruder, a shvester, iz geblibn emetsn, vi ken ikh a,

00:05:54.579 --> 00:05:59.539
ikh hob gemeynt Amerike iz der sof der velt, fertik, ver vet visn fun mir UNK ikh bin geblibn lebn?

00:05:59.719 --> 00:06:02.559
ANYWAYS, er iz a- tsurik avekgeforn un ikh bin geblibn.

00:06:02.559 --> 00:06:07.499
ikh bin aroysgegangen fun der ARMY, un ikh bin arayngegangen bay tsu di daytshn un ikh hob gebetn zol mir gebn a voynung.

00:06:07.499 --> 00:06:12.067
hot men mir gegebn tsen adresn, ikh zol mir geyn zukhn velkhe vile. in Minkhn aleyn.

00:06:12.067 --> 00:06:17.067
hob ikh gezukht, Minkhn iz geven tsehakt, nor di di forshtot iz gevezn fayn,

00:06:17.067 --> 00:06:22.977
hob ikh gegangen un ikh hob ge- ikh bin arayngekumen ershtn plats, un vu ikh hob ge- aray- arayngegangen, gezen aza sheyne vile, aza sheyne hoyz,

00:06:22.978 --> 00:06:26.730
zogt di froy, "JA, KANST MAL blaybn. bistu MAL farheyrat?" zog ikh, UNK farheyrat?

00:06:26.770 --> 00:06:30.476
ver farheyrat? ikh bin dokh gantsn gantsn yung.

00:06:30.769 --> 00:06:38.880
demolts bin ikh alt geven zibetsn un a halbn yor. loyt loyt dem loyt dem nayem TARICH vos hob ikh gegebn. ANYWAYS, dos iz gevezn

00:06:38.937 --> 00:06:42.147
un ikh bin geblibn dortn, ikh hob genumen dos hoyz,

00:06:42.147 --> 00:06:47.665
un un zi hot ge- zi hot gefregt mikh tsi zi darft aroysgeyn. vayl ikh nem iber, darfn zey aroysgeyn.

00:06:47.665 --> 00:06:55.739
keyn kinder hobn zey nisht gehat, er iz shoyn geven an elterer mentsh, er hot gearbet bay di, a a tsug firer iz er gevezn, bay di RAKEVET. a firer.

00:06:55.739 --> 00:07:02.332
hob ikh mir getrakht ven vi? ikh darf dokh say vi hobn emetsn ver s'zol kokhn, ver s'zol mir vashn, ver s'zol mir tun, ikh bin dokh a BOY aleyn. vos vel ikh zey geyn zogn, blaybts.

00:07:02.332 --> 00:07:06.999
un zey iz geven tsufridn, di gantse gas hot geredt derfun, get nor a kuk vos far a gutn mentsh zey hobn arayn gekrign,

00:07:06.999 --> 00:07:11.651
az ikh loz zey loz- az zey hobn gedorfn aroysgeyn di TSRAFIM. zog ikh, ir kent blaybn.

00:07:11.944 --> 00:07:13.440
un dort bin ikh geblibn,

00:07:13.564 --> 00:07:17.405
iz zest oys az ir ven ir volt gevolt, voltn zey aroys fun shtub?

00:07:16.973 --> 00:07:20.749
yo. ven ikh volt gevolt, geyen zey glaykh aroys. zey hobn badorfn aroysgeyn.

00:07:20.749 --> 00:07:30.166
azoy vi zey hobn mir gegebn dos tsetl hobn zey mir gezogt mir du kumst tsurik un du zogst s'gefelt dir dos hoyz, krigstu a tsetl az di kenst tsugeyn tsu der POLICE, di POLICE vet mit dir mitgeyn az zey zoln shoyn aroysgeyn.

00:07:30.166 --> 00:07:34.467
du nemst iber dos hoyz. bin ikh gegangen aleyn. ober,

00:07:34.467 --> 00:07:44.282
ikh bin dortn geblibn un ikh hob zikh farshribn oykhet tsu forn keyn Amerike, un m'hot mir ge- tsugegreyt HORIM, eltern do in Amerike, un tsu vemen ikh zol arayngeyn, vu ikh zol arayngeyn,

00:07:44.282 --> 00:07:47.541
un zey hobn mir alts erleydikt mir, un ikh hob gevart.

00:07:47.541 --> 00:07:54.134
bizkale azoy akht un fertsikstn yor, hob ikh geshvoyrn, m'hot mikh gerufn tsu der amerikaner konsul

00:07:54.134 --> 00:07:57.097
in Minkhn, un ikh hob opgeshvoyrn far Amerike,

00:07:57.097 --> 00:08:03.764
un m'hot mir gezogt mir dos iz es. gey aheym, pak di valizkes, m'veyst nisht ven der transport vet opforn, biz s'vet zayn genug mentshn

00:08:03.767 --> 00:08:06.393
vet men makhn a transport, un m'vet dikh avekshikn.

00:08:06.400 --> 00:08:11.861
ikh bin aheymgekumen, ikh hob mir tsu gepakt mir, a vokh shpeter gebn a kum aroys tsu mir tsvey khevre,

00:08:11.952 --> 00:08:18.358
fun di Hagana, fun Yisroel, tsvey ofitsirn, un kumen arayn, un redn tsu mir.

00:08:18.398 --> 00:08:30.542
mir zenen in TROUBLE, mir zenen gekumen farkhapn vos shneler di yunge khevre vos hobn zikh bafrayt brengen keyn Yisroel, untershraybn far a yor. shpeter hostu dayn rekht, kenst aroysforn, kenst forn keyn Amerike, vu du vest veln.

00:08:30.548 --> 00:08:38.666
kum HELP US, mir zenen on mentshn. di arabishe velt kemft kegn undz, un mir hobn atsind a medine vos mir viln onhaltn.

00:08:38.496 --> 00:08:40.869
ven iz dos gevezn, vos a date umgefer?

00:08:41.702 --> 00:08:45.257
dos iz gevezn in akht un fertsikstn yor.

00:08:48.469 --> 00:08:55.433
nokh eyder nokh eyder dos s'nor gevezn Palestine, tsi Yisroel?

00:08:50.468 --> 00:08:53.579
no no, m'hot p- no no, m'hot ven ven m'hot ak-

00:08:54.426 --> 00:08:58.818
no no no. ven s'shoyn geven Yisroel. m'hot shoyn d- derklert Yisroel, ISRAEL.

00:08:56.350 --> 00:08:57.238
geven Yisroel.

00:08:58.818 --> 00:09:07.188
m'hot shoyn gehert in Daytshland ISRAEL. un der un der goy hot tsu mir gezogt, zogt er, YOU HAVE YOU HAVE, zogt er, A COUNTRY, NOW YOU GOT A, zogt er, YOUR COUNTRY, A JEWISH COUNTRY, ISRAEL.

00:09:07.188 --> 00:09:11.154
in RADIO hot men ibergegebn. vu iz geven demolts TELEVISION? in di RADIOS hot men ibergegebn.

00:09:11.154 --> 00:09:15.415
un demolts un demolts ikh bin geven barn konsul, nokh akht kumen aroyf tsvey ofitsirn,

00:09:15.415 --> 00:09:22.671
un m'redt tsu mir. un ikh bin gevezn a Beytarnik, ikh bin geven a farbrenter far far Yisroel, un ikh hob lib gehat dos lebn,

00:09:22.671 --> 00:09:26.972
hob ikh gezogt, veystu vos? ikh for. mer darf men nisht redn.

00:09:27.028 --> 00:09:30.636
zog ikh, ikh gey tsu tsum konsul, UNK, un zey hobn mikh ven tsugeforn tsum konsul,

00:09:30.636 --> 00:09:33.978
az ikh zol nemen INFORMATION fun konsul, tsi der konsul vet mir zogn dos zelbe.

00:09:33.978 --> 00:09:37.285
zogt der konsul, du host rekht tsu forn a yor keyn Yisroel,

00:09:37.285 --> 00:09:41.222
un shpeter, zogt er, az du vilst farlozn, hostu di zelbe rekht. kumts tsurik, du krigst di zelbe rekht.

00:09:41.222 --> 00:09:46.111
ikh shik dikh avek, on alem, darfst gornisht batsoln. hobn zelbn plats un zelbe eltern, vest krigstu ales.

00:09:46.178 --> 00:09:53.094
vest nemen lernen dortn, far geshvoyrn hob ikh dokh shoyn gehat geshvoyrn, ales iz fertik. hot der konsulat mir gegebn a yor keyn Yisroel un kumen tsurik.

00:09:53.623 --> 00:09:56.497
hob ikh gezogt ikh bin READY. hob ikh gehat di peklekh fertik,

00:09:56.497 --> 00:10:04.147
tsvey tog shpeter iz gekumen a TRUCK, hot mikh avekgefirt in a vald arayn. dortn iz gevezn aza yu- a yidisher lager, dortn hinter Mondri- hinter MUNICH,

00:10:04.879 --> 00:10:13.524
hob ikh dortn arayngenumen un dan nakher m'hot gemakht a transport, ikh veys dort efsher a fuftsik khevre hot men aroyfgeleygt undz oyf a T- oyf a oyto MASA, UNK ikh veys nisht, a a TRUCK,

00:10:13.671 --> 00:10:15.687
un m'hot undz arayngefirt keyn Marsel.

00:10:15.687 --> 00:10:24.768
keyn Frankraykh. m'hot undz arayngefirt keyn Frankraykh, dortn iz shoyn geven a lager fun yidn vos fun iberal ver s'geforn keyn Yisroel hot men nokh do gezamlt m'zol makhn transport.

00:10:24.808 --> 00:10:27.530
un dos iz es. m'iz arayngeforn keyn Marsel,

00:10:27.530 --> 00:10:33.560
un ikh bin dortn gezisn efsher tsvey vokhn, biz m'hot tsugegreyt m'hot tsugegreyt a shif, un di shif hot geheysn Pan York,

00:10:33.735 --> 00:10:40.665
un dos iz gevezn aza shifl, aza balye, m'hot undz arayngezetst un m'hot undz geshift arayn keyn Yisroel.

00:10:40.873 --> 00:10:42.774
vifl zent ir geven oyf der shifl?

00:10:43.118 --> 00:10:48.883
vi dos vi s'geven iz geven alts in tsvey toyznt boyes mit meydlekh. iz er geven dortn.

00:10:48.923 --> 00:10:56.083
un m'hot undz arayngefirt, s'geven yene shif, a shif vos m'hot gefirt a mol ferd, khazeyrim, s'nisht vikhtik. vu m'iz gelegn iz men gelegn, s'geven gut.

00:10:56.083 --> 00:10:58.951
m'hot nisht gezukht keyn luksus, m'hot nisht gezukht keyn bakvemlekhkeytn.

00:10:58.951 --> 00:11:00.757
m'hot nor gezukht arayntsuforn keyn Yisroel.

00:11:00.757 --> 00:11:03.970
m'iz ongekumen keyn Yisroel, gedenk ikh vi haynt,

00:11:04.414 --> 00:11:08.706
hot men undz gelozt shteyn in mitn dem vaser, far der port.

00:11:08.706 --> 00:11:12.171
hot men undz oyfgezungen di Hatikva vos m'hot gezungen in Poyln,

00:11:12.733 --> 00:11:21.468
LASHUV LAARETZ, nu un do zingt men andersh. un nakher di shif tsugeforn hot men gezungen di naye Hatikva.

00:11:22.403 --> 00:11:26.312
demolts hot men undz oysgelandet, un m'hot undz bald avekgefirt.

00:11:26.908 --> 00:11:28.167
avekgefirt avu?

00:11:27.955 --> 00:11:34.622
avekgefirt, yo, UNK bald avekgefirt, tsevorfn in a in a KIBBUTZ, shnel tsevorfn in a KIBBUTZ,

00:11:34.642 --> 00:11:39.281
az m'hot undz arayngevorfn in a KIBBUTZ arayn, un bald tsu morgns iz men gegangen m'hot tsamgenumen di gantse khevre,

00:11:39.281 --> 00:11:45.060
un m'hot undz gegebn a fir arayn in a MACHANE fun di TZAVA. bay Etlit, Atlit.

00:11:45.083 --> 00:11:46.849
m'hot undz arayngefirt keyn Atlit,

00:11:46.585 --> 00:11:49.245
ir gedenkt umgefer vos a date dan iz gevezn?

00:11:49.188 --> 00:11:50.696
ver gedenkt dates?

00:11:50.635 --> 00:11:53.818
s'iz gevezn in akht un fertsik?

00:11:52.209 --> 00:11:54.357
akht un fertsik, akht un fertsik.

00:11:54.043 --> 00:11:55.758
zumer? nokhn zumer?

00:11:55.258 --> 00:11:56.332
no no, zumer.

00:11:56.372 --> 00:11:57.209
zumer.

00:11:56.862 --> 00:12:06.452
ya. hot men undz arayngefirt dortn keyn Atlit, un ikh bin arayngegangen in lager arayn un m'hot undz gehaltn bizkele m'hot undz genumen far nakht

00:12:06.452 --> 00:12:09.945
hot men undz aroysgefirt in a PARDES, un m'hot undz gelernt

00:12:09.945 --> 00:12:15.733
shisn. ver hot gehaltn a biks in der hant? zog ikh, ver hot gehaltn a biks in der hant? ver hot gehat a biks? ver veyst vos a biks?

00:12:15.733 --> 00:12:20.900
m'hot undz gelernt vi m'lodnt op, vi m'shist un vi m'shist, un vi m'tsilevet, un hin aher,

00:12:20.900 --> 00:12:26.556
far nakht vet men tseleven, arayn in azan, oyfhengen aza shildl oyf a boym in a PARDES un m'vet shisn.

00:12:26.376 --> 00:12:28.108
vi lat zent ir gevezn demolts?

00:12:28.519 --> 00:12:32.985
un demolts bin ikh shoyn gevezn alt zibetsn, akhtsn yor, nayntsn yor.

00:12:34.324 --> 00:12:37.198
un ikh bin dan arayngegangen, ikh hob ongehoybn tsu shisn,

00:12:37.198 --> 00:12:42.384
s'ge- hot er gezogt, o! a guter shiser! dos ershte mol ikh hob gegebn a shos. zogt er, bist shoyn gut!

00:12:42.610 --> 00:12:51.210
tsu morgns, m'iz gegangen, m'hot undz ongetun di kleyder, gegebn naye kleyder, a khaki kleyder, un gegebn a biksl, eynem a sten, eyner a biks,

00:12:51.587 --> 00:12:55.952
un m'hot gezogt az m'geyt aroys bay nakht oyfn front arayn.

00:12:56.852 --> 00:13:01.557
yo, un bay tog hot men geshvoyrn. m'hot geshvoyrn far MEDINAT YISRAEL,

00:13:01.557 --> 00:13:07.326
barn gebn dos gever, hot men geshvoyrn az m'vet zayn getray un azoy vayter. m'iz aroysgegangen kemfn,

00:13:07.483 --> 00:13:14.986
di nakht, di zelbe nakht m'iz aroysgegangen, iz gefaln bald tsvontsik tsvontsik khevre fun undz, fun di naye, geharget gevorn.

00:13:15.280 --> 00:13:19.577
ikh tsu morgns, ikh gey nisht mer.

00:13:19.971 --> 00:13:22.918
vos heyst, du geyst nisht? kumst UNK farkert? zogt er, ikh gey nisht mer.

00:13:22.958 --> 00:13:24.524
vos heyst du geyst nisht mer?

00:13:24.524 --> 00:13:30.579
ikh gey nisht mer in front arayn. ikh nem nisht mer keyn biks. kenst mir gebn a mashin-GUN,

00:13:31.699 --> 00:13:37.447
azoy hert di verter, kenst mir gebn a mashin-GUN, ikh bin gekumen nisht oyf keyn khasene, ikh bin gekumen in a milkhome arayn.

00:13:37.723 --> 00:13:42.391
un ikh veys az ikh bin gekumen kemfn, ikh hob oyf dem untergeshribn az ikh kum.

00:13:42.482 --> 00:13:45.682
kenst mir gebn a mashin-GUN, ikh blayb, un az nisht farloz ikh.

00:13:47.123 --> 00:13:51.828
zogt er, zog ikh, tsu vemen ken ikh redn? zogt er, muzt redn, zogt er, tsu eynem fun di greste, zogt er. vemen?

00:13:51.828 --> 00:13:57.174
muzt redn tsum SAMAL, SAMAL tsum KATZIN, biz vest ongekumen tsu dem tsu dem tsum gen- general.

00:13:59.003 --> 00:14:01.224
un s'ongekumen biz tsum general.

00:14:02.040 --> 00:14:06.253
ikh hob gezogt, ikh gey nisht mer. ikh gey nisht esn, ikh gey nisht trinken, ikh vil a mashin-GUN.

00:14:06.698 --> 00:14:09.493
ver iz geven der general? Yigal Alon.

00:14:13.026 --> 00:14:16.159
ikh zol aranysh- m'zol araynfirn dem foygl.

00:14:16.333 --> 00:14:20.203
nemt men mikh, zogt men, kenst makhn a salut? zog ikh, ikh vel makhn vi azoy ikh ken.

00:14:20.203 --> 00:14:27.094
s'den do a salut shoyn oyf oyf yidish? eyner vi ikh vel veln vel ikh makhn, oyf english, oyf poylish, oyf poylish, vi azoy ikh vel veln vel ikh makhn a salut.

00:14:27.488 --> 00:14:32.460
shtel dikh glaykh un makh a salut. m'hot mikh epes gelernt? UNK shisn, a koyl UNK oysgeshosn.

00:14:33.681 --> 00:14:38.366
geb ikh a kum arayn, shtel dikh glaykh, un gemakhn a salut, makht er mir oykhet. zogt er, SHEV.

00:14:38.558 --> 00:14:44.745
zog ikh, "ANI YACHOL LEDABER IVRIT, AVAL LO HAIVRIT KEMO SHEATA."

00:14:44.818 --> 00:14:47.984
ir hot shoyn demolts hot ir shoyn gekent a bisl hebreish, ivrit?

00:14:48.514 --> 00:14:53.860
ikh hob dokh gelernt gemore, ikh hob dokh gelernt rashes, ikh hob dokh gelernt toysfes, ikh hob dokh gelernt ales, hob, loshn koydesh.

00:14:52.142 --> 00:14:53.283
loshn koydesh.

00:14:53.860 --> 00:14:58.852
zog ikh, "ikh ken loshn koydesh, ober du redst a moderne ivrit, un dayn redn shnel ken ikh nisht farshteyn oykh.

00:14:58.909 --> 00:15:04.679
oyb azoy muztu nokh tsu mir redn yidish, vayl in a kurtser tsayt vel ikh mikh oysglaykhn, ikh vel redn mit dir di zelbe."

00:15:04.989 --> 00:15:10.293
zogt er, yidish. vos iz dayn farlang? zog ikh, "ikh ken nisht kemfn mit keyn biks.

00:15:10.587 --> 00:15:17.736
ikh bin nisht gekumen tsu keyn khasene, ikh bin gekumen tsu a milkhome, un ikh vil kemfn. kenst mir geyn a mashin-GUN?" get er mikh a kuk on,

00:15:18.990 --> 00:15:21.785
zogt er, "yingele, vi zol ikh dir nemen shoyn a mashin-GUN?"

00:15:22.635 --> 00:15:25.244
zog ikh, "dos iz an armey on a mashin-GUN?

00:15:27.175 --> 00:15:33.159
ikh darf hobn a mashin-GUN, gey ikh aroys in der milkhome arayn oyf yedn kraft un yedn, vos s'vet nor nisht fo-"

00:15:33.402 --> 00:15:42.001
zogt er, "ikh vel TRYen alts tsu tun. yetst nem tsu vos m'git dir. du bist bay mir oyf der list. azelkhe darf ikh a sakh vi dir."

00:15:42.210 --> 00:15:50.146
un klap mir di pleytse arayn, un zay a voyler BOY, un nem op ales, ikh vel dar dir da- ikh vel far dir daygen. tsu morgns hot er gebrengt a mashin-GUN.

00:15:50.146 --> 00:15:57.709
un get er a shik tsu a SAMAL, un er zol mir gebn shnel a kurs. vi azoy on tsu lodenen un vi oys tsu lodenen, un vi oyftsu- oyftsumakhn, vi tsu tsenemen,

00:15:57.709 --> 00:16:05.151
un ikh gib mikh a lern oys, in tsvey sho hob ikh gekent di toyre. oysgelernt ales. un ikh hob dos alts gemakht.

00:16:05.397 --> 00:16:13.422
un ikh hob gekemft. un ikh hob gekrign eyn medal hob ikh gekrign direkt fun Ben-Guryon.

00:16:14.172 --> 00:16:18.266
vos ikh bin nokh nisht gevezn keyn BAL-DARGA, ikh hob nokh demolts nisht gehat keyn ranges.

00:16:18.947 --> 00:16:29.977
m'iz gegangen arayn far EGYPT, hot men gehat tsu kemfn, iz geven dray groyse EMDOT fun di araber, fun di mitsrim.

00:16:30.591 --> 00:16:35.850
un m'hot dos gedorfn farnemen. az m'farnemt dos iz der veg fray.

00:16:36.092 --> 00:16:42.906
un zey hobn oyf undz geshosn, m'iz gegangen hobn zey gegebn aza fayer, ir hert, az ikh bin arayn oyf a feld,

00:16:42.906 --> 00:16:50.733
dos heyst SHETACH MET, zey shteyen oyfn barg, un zey kenen undz zen, bay nakht, ober ven m'shist

00:16:51.364 --> 00:16:56.640
zey makhn op, zey hobn oyfgemakht aza min fayer az m'hot gekent zen di mentshn oykhet.

00:16:56.663 --> 00:16:59.444
zey hobn gevorfn azelkhe vos heyst MEVAYER.

00:16:59.444 --> 00:17:06.675
un do ze ikh az m'kumt arayn in mitn feld un di mentshn loyfn tsurik. un di ofitsirn shrayen KADIMA!

00:17:06.675 --> 00:17:14.223
un m'hakt. vifl s'vet blaybn, tsu tsu der vant. az ikh loyf tsu der vant, er shteyt in der heykh, ken nisht, er ken mir shisn nor vi lang du shteyst dortn.

00:17:13.892 --> 00:17:15.691
in vos a gegnt hot ir gekemft?

00:17:15.833 --> 00:17:16.552
he?

00:17:16.238 --> 00:17:17.379
in vos a gegnt?

00:17:17.367 --> 00:17:21.327
ikh hob nor gekemft mit di egipter. nor mit di egipter.

00:17:21.486 --> 00:17:28.207
un ikh heyb mikh oyf un ikh gib a a loyf aroys, ir hert, fun di shure aroys, un gib zikh a ruk avek in der linker zayt,

00:17:28.207 --> 00:17:33.194
un ikh loyf tsu tsu der vant, tsum barg, un ikh loyf aroys oyfn barg,

00:17:33.194 --> 00:17:39.772
un der ofitsir shrayt, Pinek! ANI LO SHOMEA OTCHA. e- der eyntsiker mashin-GUN, er hert nisht er hert nisht mayn mashin arbetn.

00:17:41.280 --> 00:17:52.310
un ikh tor nisht redn. ikh loyf aroys oyfn barg, un di mashin-GUNS fun di araber klapn do oyf di khevre. zey hobn gehat di di Vikers, englisher mashinen. azoy hot es geshosn.

00:17:52.367 --> 00:18:01.878
un ikh gib mikh a khap aroyf oyfn barg un ikh shtey shoyn in di zelbe DARGA mit zey. ikh hob nor gehat eyn tash mit vos ikh bin gegangen, ikh hob gehat MISPAR SHTAYIM a tsveyter vos hot getrogn dos kestl koyln.

00:18:02.020 --> 00:18:05.861
ikh hob im oykh ibergelozt. ikh trog nor a tashme VRAZHE,

00:18:05.952 --> 00:18:12.648
dos argste darf zayn bay mir eyn tashme, a tashme fun hundert koyln. un ikh gib mir a khap aroyf oyfn barg aroyf,

00:18:12.648 --> 00:18:20.200
un ikh gib a shtel avek dem mashin-GUN un ikh gib a leyg arayn di tashme, un dos harts makht ⟨yoyre⟩, zog ikh, gotenyu, ikh zol nor matsliekh zayn.

00:18:20.300 --> 00:18:27.917
un ikh shtey direkt tsu dem KIVUN fun di araber, un ikh makh oyf di tashme un ikh shekht avek ale. ale opgehakt di kep.

00:18:28.227 --> 00:18:30.484
ale di gantse tashme arayn in dem bunker.

00:18:30.484 --> 00:18:34.126
finef shtik opgehakt vos di hobn gemakht toyt far undz.

00:18:35.297 --> 00:18:42.564
un in dem shray ikh, Mendi! tsum ofitsir, er zol aroyf. vu, EYFA ATA? zog ikh, ANI LEMALA.

00:18:42.925 --> 00:18:50.124
un krikht aroyf mit di khevre, un s'gevorn shtil. un kumt tsu tsu mir,

00:18:50.265 --> 00:18:57.043
zog ikh, yetst gey tsu mitn FLASHLIGHT, un ze tsi s'nokh do emetser lebedik dortn, efsher iz nokh emetser dortn geblibn, az du vest tsukumen vet er dikh avek shisn.

00:18:57.437 --> 00:19:02.797
un geyt mit di FLASHLIGHT un er CHECKt arum, zogt er, host ale opgeha- ale opgehakt mit di kep. ale zenen toyt.

00:19:03.394 --> 00:19:08.822
un m'hot farnumen dem gantsn EMDA, tsu morgns, m'hot gehat toyte genug,

00:19:09.199 --> 00:19:15.082
un tsu morgns iz gekumen Ben-Guryon undz VISITn, m'hot farnumen dos ales,

00:19:15.358 --> 00:19:20.347
un m'shtelt undz oys. un der der ofitsir get iber far Ben-Guryon, dos iz der boytshik.

00:19:22.615 --> 00:19:24.583
UNK

00:19:26.040 --> 00:19:34.286
un Yigal Alon iz mir gekumen shpeter tsu morgns hot mir gedankt, zogt er, ikh hob gevust, zogt er, du fest zayn mayn mayn bester khaver, mayn UNK. un er hot mikh geshikt oyf kursn,

00:19:34.815 --> 00:19:37.942
ikh bin gegangen oyf SAM- koydem kol UNK iz mem KAF,

00:19:37.942 --> 00:19:47.364
SAMAR, RAV SAMAL, RASAB, RASAR, un dan nakher bay NINETEEN SIXTY SEVEN, bin ikh shoyn gevorn ofitsir,

00:19:47.607 --> 00:19:51.819
un ongefirt mayn gantse ar- armey bay Aza.

00:19:51.657 --> 00:19:53.811
vos a vos an ofitsir zent ir gevezn?

00:19:53.884 --> 00:19:56.257
ikh bin gevezn koydem kol CHEYL RAGLI,

00:19:56.601 --> 00:20:04.070
un nakher bin ikh aribergegangen tsu tank dos, tanken, tsu ZAKHALIN, ir veyst ZAKHALIN, halb tanken.

00:20:04.870 --> 00:20:08.678
in di milkhome bay SIXTY SEVEN vos ikh hob ongefirt bin ikh gegangen mit ZACHALIN.

00:20:08.886 --> 00:20:13.790
un ir zent geven in der milkhome in der armey, dos heyst biz zibn un zekhtsik?

00:20:12.030 --> 00:20:15.510
ikh bin geven in d- ikh bin geven in dray milkhomes.

00:20:15.484 --> 00:20:18.701
ober in der armey zent ir gevezn biz zibn un zekhtsik?

00:20:18.535 --> 00:20:19.095
ya.

00:20:18.960 --> 00:20:21.215
fun akht un fertsik biz zibn un zekhtsik?

00:20:20.715 --> 00:20:25.670
ya, ober nisht keyn STEADY, ikh bin kimat mit di kursn iz oysgekumen kimat vi in STEADY.

00:20:25.693 --> 00:20:31.048
ikh bin aheymgegangen hot men tsurikgeshikt vayter oyf a kurs, ikh bin aheymgegangen hot men tsurikgeshikt vayter oyf a kurs.

00:20:31.048 --> 00:20:33.706
ober alts in eynem arayn bin ikh geven tsvontsik yor in der armey,

00:20:33.706 --> 00:20:41.331
tsvontsik yor in d- in in in Yisroel un kimat di gantse tsayt in der armey. ikh bin geven a khoydesh in der heym, un a khoydesh in TZAVA.

00:20:41.286 --> 00:20:43.288
ir hot gehat andere basheftungen?

00:20:43.530 --> 00:20:49.231
ikh hob gehat andere basheftungen. ikh hob gehat farshidene farsheftungen in Yisroel, avade hob ikh gehat farshidene farshe- ober in vos

00:20:49.231 --> 00:20:55.219
dos iz gevezn mayn ales. ikh bin gevezn tsufridn, ikh hob kha- yo, un ikh hob khasene gehat in Yisroel,

00:20:54.600 --> 00:20:59.184
 nor a khuts lomir tsurikgeyn a bisele in der tsayt

00:20:59.258 --> 00:21:06.323
ven ir zent bafrayt gevorn. zent ir zent ir tsurikgeforn in in der heym in Poyln?

00:21:06.447 --> 00:21:07.369
keyn Poyln?

00:21:08.252 --> 00:21:09.987
ikh bin gef- ikh bin geforn.

00:21:09.987 --> 00:21:18.296
ikh hob aroysgenumen a aza AWIADECTWO, aza list, fun di amerikaner un fun di rusn az ikh vil brengen mayn FAMILY.

00:21:18.296 --> 00:21:20.729
in der tsvishn der tsayt hob ikh gehert

00:21:20.729 --> 00:21:25.026
hob o- iz a mentsh ongekumen fun Rusland iz gekumen arayn keyn Daytshland, hot mir opgegebn a grus

00:21:25.026 --> 00:21:28.134
az do do do eyner a Pinek Kreyndels

00:21:28.134 --> 00:21:33.621
az du host a bruder vos er iz gekumen fun Rusland. dos iz der bruder vos iz avek keyn Rusland, hot er gezogt tsum tatn er fort avek,

00:21:33.679 --> 00:21:40.798
er iz gekumen tsurik. un er hot vayter gevoyer gevorn vayter shoyn in Poyln az ikh leb.

00:21:41.800 --> 00:21:48.864
un ven er iz avek keyn Rusland bin ikh geven azoy. un az er hot mir bafoyln nokh eyenemen az er iz gekumen un zukht mikh,

00:21:48.972 --> 00:21:54.585
ze'mir gekumen iz ongekumen tsu mir keyn Minkhn a mentsh zogn mir du host a bruder, er vart oyf dir.

00:21:54.709 --> 00:21:56.407
un for ahin im nemen.

00:21:56.312 --> 00:21:57.825
un avu hot ir im getrofn?

00:21:57.814 --> 00:22:03.968
in Min- un ikh hob, vu dem bruder? in Poyln. er hot nisht gekont ariberforn keyn Daytshland. er iz gezisn in Poyln.

00:22:03.518 --> 00:22:06.026
er iz geblibn in in Opatov?

00:22:05.796 --> 00:22:15.223
er iz geblibn nisht in Patov, in Patov hot men geharget. di di A.K. di bande hobn gehat yidn nokh der milkhome. iz er geblibn in Tsozemir, in Sandormierzh.

00:22:15.634 --> 00:22:19.966
mit zayne FRIEND, er hot gehat FRIEND, iz er geblibn in Sandormierzh. dortn iz geven a bisl mer BEZPIECZNE.

00:22:19.966 --> 00:22:27.399
mer zikhere vi in Apt. iz er geblibn dortn, un ikh heyb zikh oyf un ikh nem aroys a papir fun di amerikaner,

00:22:27.399 --> 00:22:32.432
un ikh nem aroys a papir ALSO fun danet fun fun di rusn, zey hobn nokh gearbet tsuzamen.

00:22:32.432 --> 00:22:34.199
az ikh ken forn brengen mayn FAMILY.

00:22:34.199 --> 00:22:36.865
un ikh for arayn keyn Poyln, kum ikh arayn keyn keyn Apt,

00:22:36.865 --> 00:22:41.399
ikh kum arayn keyn Apt, zogt men mir UNK du host do a bruder, vayl s'geven a por apter yidn shoyn bafrayter.

00:22:41.399 --> 00:22:43.566
un m'hot gevoynt in eyn in eyn hoyz.

00:22:43.566 --> 00:22:45.866
vu iz der bruder? in Sandormierzh.

00:22:45.705 --> 00:22:48.466
vifl yidn zenen geblibn in in Aft?

00:22:48.557 --> 00:22:52.553
ven ikh bin arayngekumen keyn Apt, dentsmol, nokh der bafrayung, demolts hob ikh getrofn,

00:22:48.945 --> 00:22:50.998
nokh nokh di bafrayung.

00:22:52.553 --> 00:22:58.864
s'gevezn mer, dos iz dokh geven bald in der BEGINNING. ven ikh bin arayngeforn keyn Apt hob ikh getrofn, demolts in dem hoyz vu ikh bin gevezn,

00:22:58.864 --> 00:23:00.616
iz gevezn zeks oder akht yidn.

00:23:01.348 --> 00:23:05.493
ober in andere erter, vifl zenen geblibn fun der gantser shtot?

00:23:06.883 --> 00:23:13.171
fun der gantser shtot? s'nisht geblibn keyn sakh. s'hot gekent efsher efsher hot gehat blaybn a hundert BOYS,

00:23:13.566 --> 00:23:18.571
vos zenen in Toronto a por yetst, do dortn, a hundert mentshn hot gekent blaybn.

00:23:18.072 --> 00:23:21.626
dos iz mentshn vos ir hot gekent? khaveyrim?

00:23:20.383 --> 00:23:26.185
vos ikh hob gekent, khaveyrim, in mayne yorn, azoy vayter, ya, ya, vos mir zenen nokh yetst oykh FRIEND.

00:23:26.185 --> 00:23:32.240
ikh hob gehat gute FRIEND vos m'iz geven in shul tsuzamen un oykh in lager tsuzamen un zey voynen yetst in Toronto.

00:23:32.010 --> 00:23:33.708
un ir halt zikh noent mit zey?

00:23:33.259 --> 00:23:34.012
ya.

00:23:34.828 --> 00:23:38.282
un ayerer bruder hot ir getrofn in Poyln? in Sandormierzh?

00:23:37.630 --> 00:23:42.284
ikh hob im getrofn in Sandormierzh, un dan bin ikh gegangen ikh hob im aribergefirt un tsurik keyn Daytshland tsu mir aheym.

00:23:42.284 --> 00:23:47.647
ober ikh hob gehat PROBLEMS mit di rusn, zey hobn mikh geshlogn, geharget, far vos ikh fir adurkh mentshn bay Tshekhn.

00:23:48.295 --> 00:23:50.215
fun Poyln arayntsuforn keyn Tshekhn.

00:23:50.215 --> 00:23:58.054
ikh fir fir mentshn. un fun Tshekhn forn arayn keyn Daytshland. dos heyst ikh nem aroys, fun der komunistisher zayt nem ikh aroys, ikh hob nisht bloyz genumen dem bruder, der bruder hot shoyn gehat geheyrat,

00:23:58.054 --> 00:24:03.933
hob ikh genumen dem bruder mit der bruder, un der bruder hot gezogt ikh hob do a gus- a gutn FRIEND Tup halt er zikh mit un er vil im oykh mitnemen.

00:24:03.946 --> 00:24:07.646
hob ikh im oykh mitgenumen, shteyt FAMILY. FAMILY iz nisht geven keyn nemen vifl.

00:24:07.650 --> 00:24:14.833
nu hobn zikh di rus, der der vakh-man bay der grenets hot zikh ongekhapt in mir un er vil mir tseraysn di papir un er hot zikh mit mir tseshlogn, ikh hob im geshlogn, er hot mikh geshlogn,

00:24:14.892 --> 00:24:20.258
der bruder iz arayn tsum komendatur, zogt er, zayt ven, zogt er, geb a kuk do shlogt men tsivile mentshn? iz aroysgegangen der komendatur,

00:24:20.258 --> 00:24:25.025
un er iz tsugelofn tsu dem CHAYAL, er hot im gekhapt er hot im arayngefirt, ikh hob im tseklapt,

00:24:25.025 --> 00:24:30.192
fun mir iz gegangen blut, fun im iz gegangen blut, hot er mikh geheysn opvishn, un im hot er aropgelozt a paker un aropgelozt in keler arayn.

00:24:30.192 --> 00:24:33.658
dem z- dem SOLDIER. un ikh hob di ale mentshn adurkhgefirt.

00:24:33.925 --> 00:24:35.775
un ir hot zey aribergefirt avu?

00:24:35.072 --> 00:24:36.905
aribergefirt arayn keyn Daytshland.

00:24:38.748 --> 00:24:43.301
un in der tsayt in der tsayt fun fun der milkhome,

00:24:42.953 --> 00:24:43.757
ya,

00:24:45.062 --> 00:24:54.675
religyez, di religye, di religyeze shtub vos ir hot farlozt in der heym, hot ir di minhogim ongehaltn, tsi,

00:24:54.242 --> 00:24:55.687
nokh nokh di milkhome nisht.

00:24:55.660 --> 00:24:57.291
in der tsayt fun der milkhome?

00:24:56.976 --> 00:25:05.593
in der tsayt iz epes andersh geven. in der tsayt fun der milkhome iz hot men gedankt got az m'hot tsu esn. ober nokh der milkhome hob ikh oyfgegebn oykh oyfgegebn di RELIGIOUS.

00:25:05.970 --> 00:25:10.739
oyfgegebn. ikh hob gezogt dos alts iz gornisht, OK vi eyner nemt dos op.

00:25:10.813 --> 00:25:15.582
az m'zol zogn, az ikh hob gekent aroysgeyn fun vald ken eyner zog- oystaytshn got hot mikh gefirt.

00:25:15.690 --> 00:25:18.969
ikh bin gelofn a gantsn tog in vald ven m'hot mikh geshosn, ikh hob nisht gezen keyn ek.

00:25:18.969 --> 00:25:21.995
un tsu morgns in tsayt in tsen minut hob ikh getrofn aroystsugeyn.

00:25:22.035 --> 00:25:31.294
treft op a a yid, a khosid, vet er es ontrefn un zogn got hot im gefirt. zol zayn a got hot im gefirt, dos iz gevezn mayn UNK. ikh veys nisht vos iz gevezn. ikh bin bald aroys. tsu morgns.

00:25:31.114 --> 00:25:33.251
iz religyez zent ir nisht geblibn.

00:25:32.937 --> 00:25:33.656
neyn.

00:25:35.215 --> 00:25:40.474
un in der tsayt vos ir zent gevezn in Daytshland, hot ir epes geton, hot ir epes gearbet?

00:25:40.497 --> 00:25:42.178
tsi ir zent gegangen in a shule?

00:25:42.184 --> 00:25:50.795
ikh bin gegangen a bisl in a shule in der Ort shule, un dan nakher hob ikh genumen ongehoybn arbetn far mir tsu makhn a por dolar, vayl m'hot dokh nisht gekent lebn ales nor vos der Unra gibt.

00:25:50.795 --> 00:25:57.689
hob ikh genumen a bisl arbetn, firn mit skhoyre, gearbet mit skhoyre, gevorn gehandlt, un THAT'S ALL. biz ikh bin avekgeforn nakher keyn Yisroel.

00:25:57.689 --> 00:25:58.935
ikh bin arayn in der armey arayn.

00:25:59.785 --> 00:26:01.044
un nokh dem,

00:25:59.818 --> 00:26:05.482
ikh hob ge- ikh hob ge- ikh hob geheyrat in Yisroel, ikh hob bakent mayn vayb dortn, un ikh hob ikh hob dray kinder geboyrn dortn,

00:26:05.269 --> 00:26:10.039
vi azoy vi azoy hot ir bagegnt ayer froy?

00:26:10.264 --> 00:26:20.568
ikh hob bagegnt mayn froy iz geven durkh a tsufal oyf a khasene, ikh bin geven oyf a khasene als als ⟨sarver⟩, bin ikh geven tsu oyf a khasene, ikh hob zi bakent, un m'hot zikh bakent fun demolts on hot men zikh genumen trefn.

00:26:20.997 --> 00:26:22.138
un m'hot geheyrat.

00:26:22.110 --> 00:26:24.382
un vi vi heyst ayer froy?

00:26:24.085 --> 00:26:24.855
Lea.

00:26:25.485 --> 00:26:27.976
Lea, vos? vos iz ir meydlsher nomen?

00:26:27.831 --> 00:26:29.715
Shmueli, Shmueli.

00:26:30.463 --> 00:26:39.772
dos heyst shoyn dos iz a ivrit nomen. der foter fun der heym hot geheysn Shmuali, panye Shmuali. un nu Shmuali oyf ivrit hot men es ibergearbet oyf Shmueli.

00:26:40.032 --> 00:26:42.068
un zi iz a geboyrene in Yisroel?

00:26:41.955 --> 00:26:44.733
mayn vayb iz gekumen mit tsvey yor alt keyn Yisroel.

00:26:44.841 --> 00:26:46.269
fun vanet iz zi gekumen?

00:26:46.663 --> 00:26:48.226
fun vanet iz zi gekumen?

00:26:47.288 --> 00:26:55.584
zey zenen gekumen, der foter iz avek nakher der foter iz avek keyn Ungarn, fun Ungarn iz er arayn keyn Rumenye un er hot dortn geheyrat,

00:26:55.843 --> 00:27:01.895
un er hot dortn gehat di kinder, nakher iz er aroyf arayngeforn. dos iz nokh far der milkhome. zey zenen nisht geven, der foter hot nisht gevust fun keyn milkhome.

00:27:01.986 --> 00:27:04.950
zey hobn nokh gevoynt dortn efsher in fuftsn tsvontsik yor far der milkhome.

00:27:05.479 --> 00:27:07.633
iz vu iz ayer froy geboyrn gevorn?

00:27:07.302 --> 00:27:08.899
in Rumenye nokh.

00:27:08.230 --> 00:27:09.422
in Rumenye.

00:27:08.922 --> 00:27:09.720
ya.

00:27:09.720 --> 00:27:11.956
zi iz arayngekumen, zi iz alt geven tsvey yor, keyn Yisroel.

00:27:12.955 --> 00:27:17.407
mir veln makhn a iberrays yetst un az m'zol kenen iberbaytn di kasete.
